  note         = {This is a pre-copyedited version of a contribution published in Shi X. ... et al (eds). Network and Parallel Computing published by Springer. The definitive authenticated version is available online via http://dx.doi.org/10.1007/978-3-319-68210-5_5. This paper was also presented at the IFIP International Conference on Network and Parallel Computing (NPC 2017), Hefei, China, 20th-21st October 2017.},
